<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV60">
<l>ceḻuṅkoḻumpe rumpaṉipo ḻintiṭavu yarntavēy</l>
<l>viḻuntularnte ḻuntuviṇpu ṭaikkumvēṅka ṭattuṇiṉ</l>
<l>ṟeḻuntiruntu tēṉporuntu pūmpoḻiṟṟa ḻaikkoḻuñ</l>
<l>ceḻuntaṭaṅku ṭantaiyuṭki ṭantamālu mallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Standing in Vēṅkaṭam where the bamboos that had risen fall down,</l>
<l rend="indent">dry up, rise [again], and pierce the skies,</l>
<l>as big dew [drops] that are pretty and fresh fall,</l>
<l>aren’t You the Māl who reclines in Kuṭantai with fertile, flourishing, flowering groves</l>
<l>—where bees rise, sit, and remain—[and] pretty ponds?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
